claim.claim-text:
A light source unit (100) comprising:
a light source (111);
a light source support (112) to hold the light source (111);
a fixing member (113) attached to the light source support (112), having a through-hole (113a) through which beams of light emitted from the light source (111) pass;
a lens holder (115) inserted into the through-hole (113a) and attached to the fixing member (113) by an adhesive; and
a collimating lens (114) to collimate the beams of light from the light source (111),
wherein attachment surfaces (115e, 115f) of the adhesive for the lens holder (115) comprise a tilted attachment surface (115f) tilted relative to an optical axis of the collimating lens (114).
